{"tid":472050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【空中畫大鵰】美海軍飛機空中畫陽具圖案 軍方稱會追究","createTime":"2017-11-17T23:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T18:36:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":304,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"c30f7f94855deec403336428b2d511caed5902b1","tid":472050,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171118/large/1510944152_b90c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171118%2Flarge%2F1510944152_b90c.jpg&h=f5506d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國海軍發表聲明，承認一架海軍飛機，曾在華盛頓州上空畫出男性生殖器官圖案。<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓州西北惠德比群島(Whidbey Island)海軍航空站的官員向當地傳媒承認，在天空以機尾噴出白煙畫出不文圖案的飛機，屬於他們的機隊。<br />\n<br />\n海軍的聲明說，海軍要求飛行員有最高標準，對此類行為完全不能接受，並認為毫無訓練價值，將追究有關飛行員。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦航空局(FAA)說，除非飛機在畫出圖案時威脅到其他人的安全，否則不能採取行動，FAA「不是道德警察」。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/美國《The Hill》"},{"pid":"bfd6a116635454e06b321f2bd5e5fe12eabe8103","tid":472050,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e63dd2e11e99031c94a3529727854ec075ecb9","tid":472050,"uid":39601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40779ce70bd96526ab8c50742a0b65f982a044a6","tid":472050,"uid":19267,"like":172,"dislike":4,"score":168,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:56:13.000Z","msg":"可以冇輔助咁喺適當嘅位轉彎畫碌鳩出嚟 個pilot都幾撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲人軍隊要重用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b55a8e9818d053f0e76ec377498f9cbe71c3ac","ti